DESCRIPTION:Testo is an extraordinary\, intimate\, and unflinchingly raw s
 olo show from Wet Mess-one of the most electrifying performers on the UK'
 s drag and theatre circuits. Blending verbatim testimony\, lip-sync\, dan
 ce\, and disorienting cabaret\, Wet Mess uses their formidable stagecraft
  to explore transmasculinity\, bodily autonomy\, queer identity\, and the
  spaces in-between. Winner of Not Another Drag Competition at London's le
 gendary Royal Vauxhall Tavern\, Mess delivers a performance that is at on
 ce grotesque and gorgeous-a visceral unraveling of binaries and a celebra
 tion of becoming.\n\nRecommended for audiences age 18+ due to nudity and 
 mature content.
DURATION:PT1H
