CONTACT;X-BEDEWORK-UID=00f1fcdb-0f068baf-010f-068baf83-00000004:None
CREATED:20251125T165952Z
DESCRIPTION:Observe world-class chamber artistry in action as the internat
 ionally acclaimed Doric String Quartet leads a public masterclass with Du
 ke students. Known for their "immaculate precision\, total unanimity\, an
 d irresistible vitality\," the Doric Quartet has earned its place among t
 he leading string quartets of their generation\, performing regularly at 
 Wigmore Hall\, the Amsterdam Concertgebouw\, Carnegie Hall\, and major fe
 stivals across Europe and the U.S.\n\nIn this interactive session\, the q
 uartet offers deep insight into the craft of chamber music-guiding studen
 ts in shaping phrasing\, refining sound and balance\, exploring character
 \, and discovering the subtle cues that transform four individual voices 
 into a unified musical conversation. Their coaching reveals the ensemble'
 s trademark blend of intellectual clarity and expressive daring\, qualiti
 es that have defined their celebrated recordings and international tourin
 g career.\n\nWhether you are a seasoned chamber music listener or simply 
 curious about how musicians collaborate at the highest level\, this maste
 rclass provides a rare window into the artistry\, communication\, and int
 erpretive decision-making that animate great performances. Hearing the Do
 ric String Quartet work closely with students in the resonant space of Ba
 ldwin Auditorium promises an inspiring and illuminating morning of music.
 \n\nFree and open to the public. All are welcome.
DURATION:PT1H30M
DTSTAMP:20260128T144951Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260328T100000
LAST-MODIFIED:20260128T144951Z
